# Psychtoolbox

## Image Pipeline

"Hook chains are per onscreen window, so each window can have a different
configuration and enable state."

See 'help PsychGLImageprocessing', "Its way to complex to use it by guessing ;)"

### Frequently Used Commands

*List all hook names*
Screen('HookFunction', [], 'ListAll')

*List all hook names for winPtr*
Screen('HookFunction', winPtr, 'ListAll')

Screen('HookFunction', winPtr, 'Query', <hook_name>, 'ListAll')

Screen('HookFunction', winPtr, 'DumpAll')

